title: Shuttler B. Sai Praneeth fails to qualify for French Open
text:
Paris: Indian shuttler B. Sai Praneeth lost in the first round of the men's singles qualifiers, failing to qualify for the main draw of the $275,000 French Open Superseries here on Tuesday.
Chinese Taipei's Wang Tzu Wei took just 36 minutes to beat Sai 21-15, 21-15 at the Stade Pierre de Coubertin.
